<title>USA: Main Street authorizes repurchase.</title>
<headline>Main Street authorizes repurchase.</headline>
<dateline>CAMPBELL, Calif. 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Main Street Athletic Clubs Inc said Friday its board had authorized the repurchase of its outstanding $6-per-share options at an equivalent price of $2 per option.</p>
<p>The offer is expected to commence May 26 and expire June 30.</p>
<p>Under the offer, an $8-per-share transaction price point is authorized, and Main Street will issue one share of common stock for each four options tendered.</p>
